Class Description
AnnotatedPea<T>
The main data structure for storing a component annotated by @Pea.
AnnotationApplicationConfig<T>
Implementation of ApplicationConfig interface providing annotation-based configuration.
ApplicationConfig
Main interface to provide configuration for an application.
AutoInject
Marks a field as to be auto injected by the JIOC dependency injection mechanism.
Pea
Indicates that the annotated class should be managed by the JIOC framework and is considered as a candidate for auto-detection when using annotation-based configuration.
XMLApplicationConfig<T>
Implementation of ApplicationConfig interface providing XML-based configuration.
XMLPea<T>
The main data structure for storing the XML pea with its corresponding fields and attributes.
